Functional

- 8x8 2 dimensional array to be defined in the class Board.
- Alpha- beta pruning
- Evaluation function: material balance/position


Non-functional
- The system should show all the valid moves available for a selected piece.(highlighted squares)
- When a piece is clicked it should highlight the piece or somehow show it is selected
- If a user uses an invalid move, display a message "invalid move"
- If a king is in check inform the user.
- Do not let the user play the move if it will cause check to happen. 
